CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper June 29, 1946, pg. 23, reads: "Class Soloist - Miss Ethel Vaughn was class soloist at Fifth Avenue High School graduation exercises at Carnegie Hall. Miss Vaughn was accompanied by Miss Jane Howard. - Harris photo."
TitMainTitle: Ethel Vaughn wearing light colored cap and gown at Fifth Avenue High School graduation
